<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY: 

The proposed rule would amend NCUA's Regulations in order to conform them to the new NCUA Fiscal and National Credit
Union Share Insurance Fund (NCUSIF) Insurance year. These changes to the fiscal and insurance years were approved
by the NCUA Board on November 15, 1993 and are effective January 1, 1995.


